cdata.name: Teachers Blockchain
cdata.desc:
Teachers Blockchain is a decentralized platform that aims to make progress in educational services around the world. The Teachers Blockchain platform helps education institutes easing the transaction and remittance services to educational institutes by collaborating with a vast of institutions. On the other hand, the platform aims to help students with a free transaction system, collaboration with different institutions, teachers and providing e-learning.

TCH is the utility token to be used in the place of FIAT or traditional currency within the Teachers Blockchain ecosystem.
